    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Vaults in which the rows of bricks are laid at a slight inclination, leaning against the previously laid row, thus obviating the need for formwork.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
